news.title: Five mixed-land use plots up for grabs near Noida airport site
news.para: While allottees can develop industry on 75% of the land allotted to them, the remaining plot can be used for setting up residential and commercial structures as well as utilities.

news.title: Mumbai: BMC gives property tax relief to only a handful
news.para: “The government directed us to give relief as people had suffered financial losses owing to Covid, and are yet to recover from it,” said municipal commissioner and now administrator Iqbal Chahal.

news.title: Noida: Install anti-smog guns, register on portal, builders told
news.para: Praveen Kumar, regional officer of UPPCB in Noida, said that the department has started sending notices to developers to ensure C&D rules are met.
